hello I'm Isis a technical customer
service associate here at the AWS office
in Dublin Ireland
today I'm going to show you how to
create delete and restore a default VPC
in Amazon virtual private Cloud let's
get started each region in your AWS
account is provided a default VPC if you
don't want to use the default VPC then
you can create a new one let's walk
through how to create a new default VPC
using the console after logging into the
AWS Management console navigate to the
VPC console
in the navigation pane choose your vpcs
choose actions and then create default
VPC
choose create default VPC and then close
the confirmation screen
before you delete a default VPC take a
look at these requirements if you delete
your default VPC then you must launch
resources in other vpcs you must first
verify that the default VPC that you
want to delete doesn't have any
resources or running Services after you
delete the VPC the services or resources
on the default VPC are no longer
available it's important to review the
default VPC components before you delete
the VPC in the AWS main landing page
enter VPC in the search bar
then choose documentation virtual
private clouds default vpcs
note the following information about
deleting a default VPC you cannot select
an existing non-default VPC as your new
default VPC also you cannot restore a
previous default VPC that you deleted
to delete your VPC using the console
after logging in to the AWS Management
console navigate to the Amazon elastic
compute Cloud console
terminate all instances in the VPC in
the navigation pane choose instances
select the instance
and then choose instant State terminate
instance
when prompted for confirmation choose
terminate
Now navigate to the VPC console
in the navigation pane choose your vpcs
select the VPC to delete and then choose
actions delete VPC
if there are resources that you must
delete or terminate before you can
delete the VPC you see them on this page
delete or terminate these resources and
then try again
finally when prompted for confirmation
click on I acknowledge that I want to
delete my default VPC enter delete
default VPC and then choose delete
so now you know how to create delete and
restore a default VPC in Amazon VPC
thanks for watching and happy cloud
computing from all of us here at AWS
